Class Channelgenerator

  • java.lang.Object

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CustomColorsProvider, Dummyprovider

    public abstract class Channelgenerator
extends Channelprovider
implements ChannellistProvider, Activatable
    This class serves as a parent for concrete implementations of a Channelprovider. It implements some basic functionality and defines some abstract methods that need to be implemented.
